[gd_scene load_steps=2 format=3]
; Scene purpose: Character creation modal with atmospheric styling — name entry, dice tumble animation, threshold-met row glow, scan-line indicator, and birth-luck tier readout.
; Review focus: verify unique node names match @onready bindings, per-row PanelContainer wraps badge/name/value/threshold cells, and ScanContainer clip_contents stays enabled.

